title: ETNIES HOLIDAY FESTIVAL 2012
description: Back again for its 9th year, the etnies Holiday Festival and shoe donation at the etnies Skatepark of Lake Forest brought in hundreds of kids to celebrate the season with Santa and the etnies team. Pierre-Andre Senizergues (etnies owner), Nick Garcia, David Reyes, Aidan Campbell, Alex Midler & Chris Del Moro were all there hanging out with the kids and giving them all a brand new pair of etnies to unwrap.
